hats <- read_csv("data/hat_observations.csv") %>%
  separate(col = "observation",
           into = c("hat_colour", "hat_type"),
           sep = ",") 
## 
##  Column specification 
## cols(
##   day = col_double(),
##   month = col_double(),

##   observation = col_character(),
##   observation_count = col_double()

Q6

hats_date_united <- hats %>% 
  unite(col = date,
        c("day", "month", "year"),
        sep = "/")

hats_date_united
hats_date_united %>% 
  filter(hat_type == "beret") %>% 
  group_by(date) %>% 
  summarise(beret_sales = sum(observation_count)) %>% 
  arrange(desc(beret_sales))
## `summarise()` ungrouping output (override with `.groups` argument)

Tidyr

Q2

exam_scores <- read_csv("data/exam_scores.csv")
## 
##  Column specification 
## cols(
##   id = col_double(),
##   exam_Q1 = col_double(),
##   exam_Q2 = col_double(),
##   exam_Q3 = col_double(),
##   exam_Q4 = col_double(),
##   exam_Q5 = col_double(),
##   exam_Q6 = col_double(),
##   exam_Q7 = col_double(),
##   exam_Q8 = col_double(),
##   exam_Q9 = col_double(),
##   exam_Q10 = col_double()
## )
exam_scores_clean <- exam_scores %>% 
  pivot_longer(cols = starts_with("exam_Q"),
               names_to = "exam_question",
               values_to = "score") %>% 
  separate(col = exam_question,
           into = c("exam", "question"),
           sep = "_Q") %>% 
  select(-exam) 

exam_scores_clean
